37 individuals who are veterans. For purposes of this subsection, "veteran" means an
38 individual who served in the United States Armed Forces and meets the definition of
39 "veteran" under 38 Code of Federal Regulations, Section 3.1 or who has served or is
40 currently serving in the Maine Army National Guard or Maine Air National Guard or the
41 Reserves of the United States Armed Forces.
